       MBS offers several Masters of Science (MSc) :
       In Marketing Management
          + Msc in Marketing
          + Msc in French Excellence, Luxury and Fashion
          + Msc in Food and Wine Management
          + Msc in Tourism and Hospitality Management
          + Msc in Digital Management
       In Finance Management
          + Msc in Finance
          + Msc in Innovative Finance
          + Msc in Responsible Finance
          + Msc in Energy and Environmental Finance
       In Business & Operations Management
          + Msc in Lean Operations Management
          + Msc in Supply Chain Management
          + Msc in Data Sciences, Big Data & A.I.
          + Msc in International Business
          + Msc in Management through Design
          + MSc in Global Business
