          + Meet us
       AACSB, EFMD and AMBA accredited, the Grande Ecole Programme (Master
       in Management) of Montpellier Business School enables graduating
       with a Masterâ€™s grade degree. It is regularly ranked among the
       World Top 50 and the French Top 15.
       To join the Grande Ecole Programme of Montpellier Business School
       means choosing to develop your talents and expertise to become an
       actor in a changing world.
