       Making a Difference
       Founded in 1897 and built on strong values, Montpellier Business
       School offers French and International talents who are unique in
       their diversity and their backgrounds, the excellency of an
       internationally recognised French Grande Ecole of Management.
       By choosing Montpellier Business School, you're choosing to become
       a responsible actor in a changing world.
       News Videos Photos Events
