       Join a Grande Ecole of Management directly after a high school
       diploma
       The Bachelor of International Business Administration Programme
       (BIBA) is an undergraduate degree (high school diploma + 3 years of
       high education), delivered over 3 years studies and recognised by
       the State (RNCP Level II), AACSB accredited and EESPIG labelled: a
       choice that prepares the future in one of the best European
       Business Schools.
